msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/name"
msgid "The Liberation of the Old"
msgstr "La liberación de lo antiguo"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/name_big"
msgid "The Liberation of the Old"
msgstr "La liberación de lo antiguo"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/story"
msgid ""
"Today, the largest airborne operation in military history takes place. "
"Nearly 17.000 airborne troops will be dropped East of the river Rhine in "
"Germany.\n"
"\n"
"You have just landed behind enemy defenses in front of Wesel, with orders to "
"secure the area in support of the planned Rhine crossing. The crossing is to "
"take place in three different locations today; you will interfere with any "
"enemy activity in the Wesel area, to prevent enemy attacks on the "
"crossings.\n"
"\n"
"Your unit, the 6th Airborne Division, will be in the very first wave. Your "
"orders are to secure the nearby train station and to clear the way for the "
"next wave."
msgstr ""
"Hoy tiene lugar la mayor operación aerotransportada de la historia militar. "
"Cerca de 17 000 soldados aerotransportados serán lanzados al este del río "
"Rin, en Alemania..\n"
"\n"
"Acabas de aterrizar detrás de las defensas enemigas frente a Wesel, con "
"órdenes de asegurar la zona en apoyo del cruce del Rin previsto. El cruce "
"tendrá lugar hoy en tres lugares diferentes; interferirás en cualquier "
"actividad enemiga en la zona de Wesel para impedir los ataques enemigos a "
"los cruces.\n"
"\n"
"Tu unidad, la 6.ª División Aerotransportada, estará en la primera oleada. "
"Tus órdenes son asegurar la estación de tren cercana y despejar el camino "
"para la siguiente oleada."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/date"
msgid "March 24th, 1945 · Near Hamminkeln, Germany"
msgstr "24 de marzo de 1945 · Cerca de Hamminkeln, Alemania"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/place"
msgid "6th Airborne Division"
msgstr "6.ª División Aerotransportada"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/outro_completed"
msgid ""
"We have restored our reputation, and the operation to cross the Rhine is a "
"huge success. Let’s see Jerry deal with this blow!\n"
"\n"
"Thank you for playing the \"Finest Hour\" campaign!"
msgstr ""
"Hemos recuperado nuestra reputación y la operación para cruzar el Rin ha "
"sido un gran éxito. ¡A ver cómo se las arregla Jerry para superar este "
"golpe! ¡Gracias por jugar a la campaña «La hora más gloriosa»!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/outro_failed"
msgid ""
"My word, that was not at all as expected. We should have held the enemy away "
"from the river crossings; but because we failed, those will probably turn "
"into a bloodbath.\n"
"\n"
"Regroup and try again!"
msgstr ""
"Vaya, eso no fue nada como esperaba. Debían haber mantenido al enemigo "
"alejado de los cruces del río, pero como fracasaron, probablemente se "
"convertirán en una masacre. ¡Reagrupen y vuelvan a intentarlo!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/part01_01"
msgid "Captain, are you alive?!"
msgstr "¡Capitán, ¿estás vivo?!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/part01_02"
msgid "On your feet, Sam, they're pushing through!"
msgstr "¡Levántate, Sam, están entrando!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/part01_03"
msgid "Hold your ground!"
msgstr "¡Mantén tu posición!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/part01_04"
msgid "Ammo running low… We won’t be holding this junkyard here for long."
msgstr ""
"Se está acabando la munición... No aguantaréis mucho tiempo en este "
"vertedero."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/part01_05"
msgid "A Jerry’s tank incoming! Bloody hell… We don’t have PIATs, do we?"
msgstr "¡Se acerca un tanque Jerry! Maldita sea... No tenéis PIAT, ¿verdad?"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/part01_06"
msgid ""
"Our little Locust has arrived to support us! Just in time. Keep holding the "
"ground! Crew, destroy this tank!"
msgstr ""
"¡Nuestro pequeño Locust ha llegado para apoyarnos! Justo a tiempo. ¡Mantened "
"la posición! ¡Equipo, destruid este tanque!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/part01_07"
msgid "Nice hit! Come on, Jerry, we have plenty of shells for all of you!"
msgstr "¡Buen golpe! ¡Vamos, Jerry, tenemos munición suficiente para todos!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/part01_08"
msgid "Alright, we’re good for now. Let’s check where we are on the map…"
msgstr "Muy bien, por ahora estamos bien. Veamos dónde estamos en el mapa..."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/part01_wounded_01"
msgid ""
"What the hell is doc up to? Go help our wounded lads, they have one foot in "
"the grave!"
msgstr ""
"¿Qué demonios está haciendo el doctor? ¡Ve a ayudar a nuestros muchachos "
"heridos, están a punto de morir!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/part01_wounded_02"
msgid ""
"For God’s sake, don’t be like a shy nurse! Tend to the wounded! They won’t "
"hold for long!"
msgstr ""
"¡Por el amor de Dios, no seas como una enfermera tímida! ¡Atiende a los "
"heridos! ¡No aguantarán mucho más!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/part01_wounded_03"
msgid ""
"Good, now back to fighting! There should be some crates near the glider, top "
"up your ammo!"
msgstr ""
"¡Bien, ahora volvamos a la lucha! Debería haber algunas cajas cerca del "
"planeador, ¡reponed munición!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/part01_wounded_04"
msgid "For Christ's sake, we could have saved them!"
msgstr "¡Por el amor de Dios, podríamos haberlos salvado!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/part01_pl_armor_destroyed"
msgid "They’ve destroyed our Locust! I reckon it’s just us now against Jerry."
msgstr ""
"¡Han destruido nuestro Locust! Supongo que ahora solo quedamos nosotros "
"contra Jerry."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/part02_01"
msgid ""
"Believe it or not, this is the first time our pilots skipped on the ale and "
"they dropped us exactly on target. We have to destroy Jerry's anti-air and "
"secure the nearby rail station."
msgstr ""
"Aunque parezca increíble, es la primera vez que nuestros pilotos no se han "
"emborrachado y nos han dejado justo en el objetivo. Tenemos que destruir la "
"defensa antiaérea de Jerry y asegurar la estación de tren cercana."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/part02_02"
msgid ""
"Right in front of us there is a first anti-air position. Knocking it out "
"will save our gliders so they can drop us some toys. Makes sense to take it "
"out first."
msgstr ""
"Justo delante de nosotros hay una primera posición antiaérea. Si la "
"destruimos, salvaremos nuestros planeadores y podrán lanzarnos algunos "
"juguetes. Tiene sentido eliminarla primero."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/part02_03"
msgid ""
"If the maps are still up to date, there should be more ack-ack guns at the "
"railway station. You know the drill, lads."
msgstr ""
"Si los mapas siguen estando actualizados, debería haber más cañones "
"antiaéreos en la estación de tren. Ya sabéis lo que hay que hacer, muchachos."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/part02_04"
msgid ""
"Another company landed to our west. They will support our little offensive."
msgstr ""
"Otra compañía ha aterrizado al oeste. Apoyarán nuestra pequeña ofensiva."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/part02_05"
msgid ""
"Those signs slightly concern me. Good thing we have mine detectors in the "
"supply box at the glider, making it walk in the park. Defusing will take a "
"lot of time, though."
msgstr ""
"Esas señales me preocupan un poco. Menos mal que tenemos detectores de minas "
"en la caja de suministros del planeador, lo que hace que sea pan comido. Sin "
"embargo, desactivarlas llevará mucho tiempo."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/part02_06"
msgid "Hold fire, hold your damn fire! They’re surrendering!"
msgstr "¡No dispares, no dispares, maldita sea! ¡Se están rindiendo!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/part02_gun_destroyed_01"
msgid "One gun down! Let’s get on to the other one!"
msgstr "¡Una pistola menos! ¡Pasemos a la otra!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/part02_gun_destroyed_02"
msgid ""
"Both guns have been destroyed! We should get some reinforcements from our "
"landing zone very soon."
msgstr ""
"¡Las dos armas han sido destruidas! Deberíamos recibir refuerzos desde "
"nuestra zona de aterrizaje muy pronto."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/part02_pl_see_88"
msgid ""
"Heads up, there is an 88’ to the north of us at the railway station! Try to "
"avoid its field of view for now."
msgstr ""
"¡Atención, hay un 88 al norte de nosotros, en la estación de tren! Intentad "
"evitar su campo de visión por ahora."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/part02_near_train"
msgid ""
"Look at that, this tank destroyer should be still working. But how can we "
"get to it?"
msgstr ""
"Mira eso, este cazacarros debería seguir funcionando. Pero, ¿cómo podemos "
"llegar hasta él?"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/part02_crewed_locomotive"
msgid ""
"Did I ever tell you that it was my dream to become a train driver? Well, "
"because it wasn’t. Still can't believe some people like them and not get "
"bored."
msgstr ""
"¿Te he contado alguna vez que mi sueño era ser maquinista de tren? Pues no, "
"porque no era así. Todavía no puedo creer que a algunas personas les guste y "
"no se aburran."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/part02_linked_wagon"
msgid "I better get promoted for this…"
msgstr "Más vale que me asciendan por esto..."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/part02_crewed_secret"
msgid ""
"Blimey, this thing is pristine! Well, beside the gun but it’s negotiable "
"with a good repair kit."
msgstr ""
"¡Caramba, esto está impecable! Bueno, excepto por la pistola, pero eso se "
"puede solucionar con un buen kit de reparación."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/cutscene/pause_01"
msgid "You know, I sort of envy them."
msgstr "Sabes, en cierto modo os envidio."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/cutscene/pause_02"
msgid "What do you mean?"
msgstr "¿Qué quieres decir?"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/cutscene/pause_03"
msgid ""
"These Germans. Their chances of getting home alive are better than ours."
msgstr ""
"Estos alemanes. Sus posibilidades de volver a casa con vida son mejores que "
"las vuestras."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/cutscene/pause_04"
msgid ""
"Look at this boy… I wouldn’t give him 16. At his age, I used to shoot a "
"slingshot at abandoned buildings windows and run away from the coppers… This "
"poor kid was running around with a damn rifle a half hour ago… What is the "
"world coming to?.."
msgstr ""
"Mira a este chico... No le daría ni 16 años. A su edad, yo solía disparar "
"con una honda a las ventanas de edificios abandonados y huir de la "
"policía... Este pobre chico estaba corriendo con un maldito rifle hace media "
"hora... ¿A dónde va a parar el mundo?.."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/cutscene/pause_05"
msgid ""
"At your age? Do you mean the period between the Roman Empire and the Hundred "
"Years' War?"
msgstr ""
"¿A tu edad? ¿Te refieres al periodo comprendido entre el Imperio romano y la "
"Guerra de los Cien Años?"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/cutscene/pause_06"
msgid ""
"Knock it off, will ya? I’m not that old actually. Turned 32 recently. This "
"morning, more specifically."
msgstr ""
"¿Quieres dejarlo ya? En realidad no soy tan mayor. Acabo de cumplir 32 años. "
"Esta mañana, para ser más exactos."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/cutscene/pause_07"
msgid ""
"Are you having a laugh?! Keeping this secret the whole time? Happy birthday, "
"my ancient friend."
msgstr ""
"¿¡Te estás riendo?! ¿¡Manteniendo este secreto todo este tiempo! Feliz "
"cumpleaños, mi viejo amigo."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/cutscene/pause_08"
msgid "Appreciate it, mate."
msgstr "Te lo agradezco, amigo."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/cutscene/pause_09"
msgid ""
"Captain, we just got a message from the US 17th! They’ve managed to secure "
"the bridge but Jerry is pushing ‘em very hard. They’re requesting assistance "
"from us."
msgstr ""
"Capitán, ¡acabamos de recibir un mensaje de la 17.ª División de los Estados "
"Unidos! Han conseguido asegurar el puente, pero los alemanes los están "
"presionando mucho. Solicitan vuestra ayuda."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/cutscene/pause_10"
msgid ""
"Alright lads, the celebration is postponed. Sergeant Shelton, you stay here "
"and make sure not a single Jerry holding a weapon comes close to the railway "
"station. Try to find something to drink while we’re away. I’ll take the "
"second platoon and move towards the Yankee positions."
msgstr ""
"Muy bien, muchachos, la celebración queda pospuesta. Sargento Shelton, "
"quédate aquí y asegúrate de que ningún alemán armado se acerque a la "
"estación de tren. Intenta encontrar algo de beber mientras estamos fuera. Yo "
"me llevaré al segundo pelotón y avanzaré hacia las posiciones yanquis."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/cutscene/pause_11"
msgid "Got it, Sir. Good luck. See you on the other side."
msgstr "Entendido, señor. Buena suerte. Nos vemos al otro lado."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/part03_01"
msgid ""
"The Yanks have managed to capture the bridge on the Issel river but Jerry is "
"counterattacking. We need to support the GIs quickly."
msgstr ""
"Los yanquis han conseguido tomar el puente sobre el río Issel, pero Jerry "
"está contraatacando. Tenemos que apoyar rápidamente a los soldados "
"estadounidenses."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/part03_02"
msgid ""
"Spread out and watch the flanks! Our ground forces should be here soon. Hold "
"your ground!"
msgstr ""
"¡Dispersaos y vigilad los flancos! Nuestras fuerzas terrestres deberían "
"llegar pronto. ¡Mantened vuestras posiciones!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/part03_03"
msgid "They are not as cooperative as the ones at the railway station, ha?"
msgstr "No son tan cooperativos como los de la estación de tren, ¿verdad?"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/part03_04"
msgid ""
"What the… Holy shit, where did they come from?! Watch the southern flank!"
msgstr "¿Qué demonios...? ¡¿De dónde han salido?! ¡Cuidado con el flanco sur!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/part03_05"
msgid "Everyone! Fall back!"
msgstr "¡Todos! ¡Retrocedan!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/part03_ally_mgun_crew_dead"
msgid "Someone man this HMG, that machinegunner is down!"
msgstr "¡Que alguien maneje esta ametralladora pesada, el artillero ha caído!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/part03_armor_01"
msgid "Watch out, enemy tank from the east!"
msgstr "¡Cuidado, tanque enemigo desde el este!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/part03_armor_02"
msgid "Eyes on the south-east! They’ve brought another tank!"
msgstr "¡Atentos al sureste! ¡Han traído otro tanque!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/part03_armor_03"
msgid "Another tank! Main road!"
msgstr "¡Otro tanque! ¡Carretera principal!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/part03_mortar_firing"
msgid ""
"German mortar is firing at us from the east! Shut it down already, God "
"dammit!"
msgstr ""
"¡Un mortero alemán nos está disparando desde el este! ¡Apáguenlo ya, maldita "
"sea!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/cutscene/tankman_01"
msgid ""
"What in Gordon Benett are you looking for in that shed, Mac? Come and help "
"us already!"
msgstr ""
"¿Qué demonios estás buscando en ese cobertizo, Mac? ¡Ven a ayudarnos de una "
"vez!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/cutscene/tankman_02"
msgid "You scrooges cannot be that greedy, can you, lads?"
msgstr "Ustedes, tacaños, no pueden ser tan codiciosos, ¿verdad, muchachos?"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/cutscene/tankman_03"
msgid ""
"There's no way on this earth you downed all the bloody bottles yourself!"
msgstr ""
"¡No hay forma en este mundo de que te hayas bebido todas esas malditas "
"botellas tú solo!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/cutscene/tankman_04"
msgid ""
"For the love of God, if you’re doing this shit again, I’m gonna leave you to "
"rot with the other Boche!"
msgstr ""
"Por el amor de Dios, si vuelves a hacer esta mierda, ¡te voy a dejar "
"pudrirte con los demás boches!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/cutscene/tankman_05"
msgid ""
"Oi, hello my dear friend, nice to see you. It won’t be long, unfortunately. "
"But we’ll have a very good time together, you have my word. Yeah, I’m coming!"
msgstr ""
"Hola, querido amigo, me alegro de verte. Por desgracia, no será por mucho "
"tiempo. Pero lo pasaremos muy bien juntos, te lo prometo. ¡Sí, voy!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/cutscene/tankman_06"
msgid ""
"Christ alive, what have I done to deserve such punishment? Get rid of that "
"crate and help us, God dammit!"
msgstr ""
"Por Dios, ¿qué he hecho para merecer tal castigo? ¡Deshazte de esa caja y "
"ayúdanos, maldita sea!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/part04_01"
msgid ""
"The engine doesn’t start, I need you to help us fix it. These poor airborne "
"blokes are still under Boche’s fire and we have to get to this bridge as "
"soon as possible."
msgstr ""
"El motor no arranca, necesito que nos ayudes a arreglarlo. Estos pobres "
"muchachos siguen bajo el fuego enemigo y tenemos que llegar al puente lo "
"antes posible."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/part04_02"
msgid ""
"You lads are mean to me, you know that? I try my best to keep the… What did "
"they call it?.. Ehm… Esprit de corps! Yeah, the esprit de corps thing! I put "
"my heart into this crew so we’re all blythe together."
msgstr ""
"Chicos, sois muy crueles conmigo, ¿lo sabéis? Yo hago todo lo posible por "
"mantener el... ¿Cómo se llama?... Eh... ¡El espíritu de equipo! Sí, ¡el "
"espíritu de equipo! Me esfuerzo mucho por que este equipo funcione bien y "
"todos estemos contentos juntos."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/part04_03"
msgid ""
"And nobody has ever appreciated what I do for you, lads. I mean… I’m not the "
"most bonnie lad in the world, so they’ve told me… But… Nobody?"
msgstr ""
"Y nadie ha apreciado nunca lo que hago por ustedes, muchachos. Quiero "
"decir... No soy el chico más guapo del mundo, eso es lo que me han dicho... "
"Pero... ¿Nadie?"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/part04_04"
msgid ""
"Mate, listen… Not a soul has ever had a sip of your booze except yourself."
msgstr "Amigo, escucha... Nadie más que tú ha probado tu alcohol."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/part04_05"
msgid "That’s not true."
msgstr "Eso no es cierto."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/part04_06"
msgid "God help us… Just shut your mouth and get to work, Mac!"
msgstr "Que Dios nos ayude... ¡Cierra la boca y ponte a trabajar, Mac!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/part04_07"
msgid ""
"Aight men, we’re good to go! Tank crews, take your positions! Infantry, all "
"aboard! Time to save our paras!"
msgstr ""
"¡Muy bien, chicos, estamos listos para partir! ¡Tripulaciones de los "
"tanques, tomad vuestras posiciones! ¡Infantería, todos a bordo! ¡Es hora de "
"salvar a nuestros paracaidistas!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/part04_08"
msgid ""
"I see enemy armor! 200 yards, north-east! All units, load AP! Drivers, take "
"cover behind the tank wreckages!"
msgstr ""
"¡Veo blindados enemigos! ¡A 200 metros, al noreste! ¡Todas las unidades, "
"carguen AP! ¡Conductores, pónganse a cubierto detrás de los restos de los "
"tanques!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/part04_09"
msgid "Targets incoming from the north! Gunner, traverse!"
msgstr "¡Objetivos entrando por el norte! ¡Artillero, gira el cañón!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/part04_10"
msgid "I see more tanks from the north-west!"
msgstr "¡Veo más tanques desde el noroeste!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/part04_11"
msgid "Where in the hell do they come from?!"
msgstr "¿De dónde demonios salen?"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/part04_12"
msgid "More enemy tanks from the north, get ready!"
msgstr "¡Más tanques enemigos desde el norte, prepárate!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/part04_13"
msgid ""
"I think that was the last of them. Brilliant job, gents. Let’s keep moving "
"to the Issel bridge. If someone needs a repair, do it now. There won’t be a "
"way back."
msgstr ""
"Creo que ese era el último. Excelente trabajo, señores. Sigamos avanzando "
"hacia el puente Issel. Si alguien necesita repararse, que lo haga ahora. No "
"habrá vuelta atrás."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/part04_14"
msgid "They’re still alive! We should help them!"
msgstr "¡Aún están vivos! ¡Debemos ayudarles!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/part04_15"
msgid "Priority targets to the south-west! Three tigers! Everyone, load APDS!"
msgstr ""
"¡Objetivos prioritarios al suroeste! ¡Tres tigres! ¡Carguen APDS, todos!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/part04_16"
msgid ""
"Just look who showed up at the last moment! Hold your ground, we’re not "
"falling back!"
msgstr ""
"¡Mira quién ha aparecido en el último momento! ¡Mantén tu posición, no vamos "
"a retroceder!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/part04_17"
msgid "All armoured targets have been destroyed! Brilliant job, gents."
msgstr ""
"¡Todos los objetivos blindados han sido destruidos! Excelente trabajo, "
"señores."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/part04_18"
msgid "They’re falling back! I’ll be damned… We did it… We did it, lads…"
msgstr ""
"¡Están retrocediendo! Que me parta un rayo... Lo hemos conseguido... Lo "
"hemos conseguido, muchachos..."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/cutscene/outro_01"
msgid ""
"So I reckon that’s where our war ends too, my friend. Did you manage to find "
"the hush-hush supplies I asked you?"
msgstr ""
"Así que supongo que ahí es donde termina nuestra guerra también, amigo mío. "
"¿Conseguiste encontrar los suministros secretos que te pedí?"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/cutscene/outro_02"
msgid "Well… I’m afraid I did not."
msgstr "Bueno... Me temo que no."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/cutscene/outro_03"
msgid ""
"I’m extremely disappointed, Sir Fletcher. You will only get the next "
"promotion over my dead body."
msgstr ""
"Estoy muy decepcionado, señor Fletcher. Solo conseguirás el próximo ascenso "
"por encima de mi cadáver."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/cutscene/outro_04"
msgid ""
"Lieutenant Leonard Hall, this is my modest company. You’ve made it really "
"good there."
msgstr ""
"Teniente Leonard Hall, esta es mi modesta compañía. Lo has hecho muy bien."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/cutscene/outro_05"
msgid ""
"It’s Captain Samuel Rowse who is thankful to your men till his last day."
msgstr ""
"Es el capitán Samuel Rowse quien está agradecido a tus hombres hasta el "
"último día de su vida."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/cutscene/outro_06"
msgid "You lads look sad. Think I know how to cheer you up."
msgstr "Chicos, parecéis tristes. Creo que sé cómo animaros."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/cutscene/outro_07"
msgid "Mac, get your arse over here! And bring the thing you’ve found!"
msgstr "¡Mac, ven aquí! ¡Y trae lo que has encontrado!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/cutscene/outro_08"
msgid ""
"Sir, with all due respect… But I think we just need some rest. It’s been a "
"really tough day with all the…"
msgstr ""
"Señor, con todo respeto... Pero creo que solo necesitamos descansar un poco. "
"Ha sido un día muy duro con todo lo que ha pasado..."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/cutscene/outro_09"
msgid "Blimey… You've read our minds, lieutenant!"
msgstr "¡Caramba... nos ha leído el pensamiento, teniente!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/cutscene/outro_10"
msgid ""
"Sir, I’ve told you I would share my findings. Let me introduce some of "
"Jerry’s homemade booze to you, lads. Tastes like a cough syrup but still "
"warms you right up."
msgstr ""
"Señor, te dije que compartiría mis hallazgos. Chicos, permítanme "
"presentarles el licor casero de Jerry. Sabe a jarabe para la tos, pero te "
"calienta muy bien."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/cutscene/outro_11"
msgid "Ehm… I beg your pardon?"
msgstr "Eh... ¿Perdón?"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/cutscene/outro_12"
msgid ""
"This is private MacKenzie, we call him just Mac. He is a good bloke from a "
"far northern village. Don’t worry, most of us can’t understand him anyway."
msgstr ""
"Este es el soldado MacKenzie, al que llamamos simplemente Mac. Es un buen "
"tipo de un pueblo del extremo norte. No te preocupes, la mayoría de nosotros "
"no le entendemos de todos modos."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/cutscene/outro_13"
msgid ""
"I don’t think that will be a problem. I bet we all speak Scottish after a "
"few shots."
msgstr ""
"No creo que eso sea un problema. Apuesto a que todos hablaremos escocés "
"después de unos tragos."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/cutscene/outro_14"
msgid "Alright, let’s find out what that Jerry booze tastes like. Cheers!"
msgstr "Muy bien, veamos qué sabor tiene ese licor Jerry. ¡Salud!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/cutscene/outro_15"
msgid "Cheers, lads!"
msgstr "¡Salud, chicos!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/cutscene/outro_16"
msgid "Cheers!"
msgstr "Salute!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/cutscene/outro_17"
msgid "Bottoms up!"
msgstr "¡Hasta el fondo!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/part04_enemy_destroyed_01"
msgid "Panzer down! Gunner, service the next target!"
msgstr "¡Tanque derribado! ¡Artillero, apunta al siguiente objetivo!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/part04_enemy_destroyed_02"
msgid "Good hit, he is burning!"
msgstr "¡Buen golpe, está ardiendo!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/part04_enemy_destroyed_03"
msgid "Target destroyed!"
msgstr "¡Objetivo destruido!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/part04_enemy_destroyed_04"
msgid "He’s done for!"
msgstr "¡Está acabado!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/part04_enemy_destroyed_05"
msgid "Another armor taken out!"
msgstr "¡Otra armadura eliminada!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/part04_enemy_destroyed_06"
msgid "One more Panzer down!"
msgstr "¡Un Panzer más derribado!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/part04_enemy_destroyed_07"
msgid "Good hit!"
msgstr "¡Buen golpe!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/"
"part04_friendly_destroyed_01"
msgid "Atkinson’s tank is burning!"
msgstr "¡El tanque de Atkinson está en llamas!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/"
"part04_friendly_destroyed_02"
msgid "Johnson! We lost him!"
msgstr "¡Johnson! ¡Lo hemos perdido!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/"
"part04_friendly_destroyed_03"
msgid "McLeon’s crew is down!"
msgstr "¡La tripulación de McLeon ha caído!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/part04_at_guns"
msgid "Ambush! AT-guns, 170 yards to the north!"
msgstr "¡Emboscada! ¡Cañones antitanque a 170 yardas al norte!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/narrator/part04_at_inf"
msgid "Watch out, watch out, AT infantry from the west!"
msgstr "¡Cuidado, cuidado, infantería AT desde el oeste!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/ui/hint_locomotive"
msgid ""
"While driving the locomotive, you can <c(B29557)>couple it to other wagons</"
"c> when approaching them."
msgstr ""
"Mientras conduces la locomotora, puedes <c(B29557)>acoplarla a otros "
"vagones</c> al acercarte a ellos."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/ui/hint_switch"
msgid ""
"You can change the direction of a <c(B29557)>railway switch</c> by selecting "
"an infantry unit and right-clicking on the switch."
msgstr ""
"Puedes cambiar la dirección de un cambio de vía e <c(B29557)></c> "
"seleccionando una unidad de infantería y haciendo clic con el botón derecho "
"del ratón sobre el cambio."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/ui/scenario_tankman_text"
msgid "At the same time. 2km from Issel bridge."
msgstr "Al mismo tiempo. A 2 km del puente de Issel."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/ui/scenario_tankman_text_empty"
msgid ""
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/tasks/01_landing"
msgid "Survive the German counter-attack"
msgstr "Sobrevive al contraataque alemán."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/tasks/02_antiair"
msgid ""
"Secure the anti-air positions near the Landing Zone to receive reinforcements"
msgstr ""
"Asegura las posiciones antiaéreas cerca de la zona de aterrizaje para "
"recibir refuerzos."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/tasks/03_station"
msgid "Cut German supply lines by securing the Railway Station"
msgstr ""
"Corta las líneas de suministro alemanas asegurando la estación de tren."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/tasks/04_bridge"
msgid "Assist the 17th US airborne division on the Issel Bridge"
msgstr ""
"Ayudar a la 17.ª división aerotransportada estadounidense en el puente de "
"Issel."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/tasks/05_schnapps"
msgid "Put the Schnapps crate into the Comet's inventory"
msgstr "Pon la caja de aguardiente en el inventario del Comet."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/tasks/06_repair"
msgid "Repair the Comet tank"
msgstr "Repara el tanque Comet."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/tasks/07_advance"
msgid "Advance towards the Issel Bridge to help the paratroopers"
msgstr "Avanza hacia el puente Issel para ayudar a los paracaidistas."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/tasks/08_comet"
msgid "Comet tank must survive"
msgstr "El tanque Comet debe sobrevivir."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/tasks/09_tanks"
msgid "Survive the German ambush"
msgstr "Sobrevive a la emboscada alemana."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/tasks/10_remains"
msgid "Eliminate remaining German forces"
msgstr "Eliminar las fuerzas alemanas restantes."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/tasks/opt01_heal"
msgid "Heal the wounded paratroopers"
msgstr "Cura a los paracaidistas heridos."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/tasks/secret01"
msgid "Secret objective #1"
msgstr "Objetivo secreto nº 1"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/tasks/secret01_completed"
msgid ""
"Secret objective: Fare Dodger - Solve the railway puzzle and capture the tank"
msgstr ""
"Objetivo secreto: Fare Dodger: resuelve el rompecabezas ferroviario y "
"captura el tanque."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/tasks/secret02"
msgid "Secret objective #2"
msgstr "Objetivo secreto n.º 2"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1945_03_24_varsity/tasks/secret02_completed"
msgid ""
"Secret objective: Hangover - Put all available Schnapps crates into the "
"Comet inventory"
msgstr ""
"Objetivo secreto: Resaca: coloca todas las cajas de aguardiente disponibles "
"en el inventario del Comet."
